definitions.title: Def
definitions.body: II. [[אול]], [[איל]] (be in front of, precede, lead; v. Thes Nö:MBA 1880, 774; SBA 1882, 1175, who comp. Ar 0’aw=alu for 0a0walu, Targ. [[אוולא]]; cf. Sab. [[אול]] DHM:Epigr. Denkm. 33. 34; v. on the other hand Lag:Or ii. p. 3; M i. p.100 & sub I. [[אלה]] infr.)
